Simple IM v1.0.0

Release Date: 2025-11-07
Build: Initial Release

Features:

- User Authentication (Register/Login)
- Friend Management (Add/Remove/List)
- Private Chat (1-to-1 Messaging)
- Group Chat (Multi-user Messaging)
- WebSocket Real-time Communication
- Message Status Management (Read/Unread)
- Online Status Detection
- JWT Token Authentication
- Redis PubSub Message Distribution

Tech Stack:

- Go 1.21+
- Gin Web Framework
- MySQL 8.0 (GORM)
- Redis 7.0
- WebSocket (Gorilla)
- JWT Authentication
- Zap Logger

Architecture:

- Layered Architecture (Handler -> Service -> Repository)
- Dual Server Model (HTTP + WebSocket)
- Microservice Ready
- Docker Support

Author: Simple IM Team
License: MIT
